Class Connector

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database.DbObject
      • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.jcomparser.saving.Connector

  • public class Connector
extends DbObject
    The Connector has methods to create entries inside the database. Therefore it uses the database.ConnectionWrapper class.
